{"tid":1593172,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新增工具：散銀包","createTime":"2019-09-25T03:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T07:52:30.000Z","uid":215950,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f047c281485271edc42d0aca2ad79c57eff1109","tid":1593172,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"提提大家，散銀包有好多用途：<br />\n<br />\n1. 八達通係由幾間主要運輸公司做股東既，你用八達通消費係直接輸送利益比佢地<br />\n<br />\n2. 散銀冇得 gps 定位，冇得追蹤數據<br />\n<br />\n3. 比散銀掟到會好痛，話散都係金屬，請好好保管。 如果碰撞金屬頭盔仲會令人產生混亂，因為好響又有震動。<br />\n<br />\n4. 如果啲神沙生銹，可以用 WD40 清理一下，但掉左落地好易跣親，要小心呀<br />\n<br />\n5. 帶散銀出街冇可能係犯法<br />\n<br />\n6. 好多公司已經淘汰左處理散銀既工具同人手，突然多咁多散銀要處理，其實會打擊經濟。"},{"pid":"74db08b6de73eb2fce1834f8376f29ab52d0763a","tid":1593172,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"f83cf8e9a77b6508da527ca1d8e4cb13dfec07cc","tid":1593172,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:07:36.000Z","msg":"［警世］有無人記得當年文宣遍地開花既盛況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593125</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13f23c4fef0127bab5f939b432775ab1bb3743e6","tid":1593172,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"加隻長襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4856d9e98c9bb42411b21f4752b16867cd3b0122","tid":1593172,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"13f23c4fef0127bab5f939b432775ab1bb3743e6","tid":1593172,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"加隻長襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig